<sect1 id="dir_bf15dcce3b0eb2b2bde353446d930b9c_1autotoc_md416">
<title>helios::engine::modules::ui</title><para>User interface components and systems for game entities.</para>
<para>This module provides components and systems for creating and managing UI elements within the helios engine. It supports viewport-relative positioning, text rendering, and data binding between game state and UI components.</para>
</sect1>
